Mahewin-wmfs-status is a project, for display information in a wmfs
status bar. It is written in Perl language.

For install it download status.pl and put in .config/wmfs/.

Configure

    In a wmfsrc:
    status_path   = .config/wmfs/status.pl
    status_timing = 1

    To set mahewin-wmfs-status, you can look at the example configuration.
    Put in .config/wmfs/ directory.

DEPENDENCIES
    Sys::Statistics::Linux
    Config::IniFiles

BUGS AND LIMITATIONS
    None. I hope.

THANKS
    Thanks to Martin Duquesnoy for wmfs.

